OL,3,CGovernment denies Chagos Island deal
OL,4,Cis paused after Trump criticism
OL,6,FThe government has denied that the
OL,7,FChagos Island deal has been paused
OL,8,Fafter a minister appeared to suggest
OL,9,Fthe UK was putting on hold to discuss
OL,10,Fit with the United States following
OL,11,Fcriticism by Donald Trump.
OL,13,FThe #35 billion deal, which includes a
OL,14,Fplan to lease back the UK-US Diego
OL,15,FGarcia military base, has been heavily
OL,16,Fcriticised by the US president,
OL,17,Fdespite previous statements that
OL,18,FWashington backed it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
