OL,3,CGovernment denies Chagos Island deal
OL,4,Cis paused after Trump criticism
OL,6,FForeign Office minister Hamish
OL,7,FFalconer said the US had backed the
OL,8,Fdeal but that there had been a "very
OL,9,Fsignificant" statement from the
OL,10,FAmerican president since then.
OL,12,FTrump has described the deal as a "big
OL,13,Fmistake" and urged Sir Keir Starmer:
OL,14,F"Do not give away Diego Garcia."
OL,16,FThe legislation going through
OL,17,FParliament will ratify a treaty to
OL,18,Fhand over the Chagos Islands ` the
OL,19,FBritish Indian Ocean Territory ` to
OL,20,FMauritius.
