OL,3,CGovernment denies Chagos Island deal
OL,4,Cis paused after Trump criticism
OL,6,FThe government has argued the deal is
OL,7,Fnecessary to guarantee the future of
OL,8,Fthe Diego Garcia base after an
OL,9,Fadvisory International Court of
OL,10,FJustice ruling in 2019 backed
OL,11,FMauritian claims to sovereignty over
OL,12,Fthe islands.
OL,14,FUnder the plan, the UK will pay #34.7
OL,15,Fbillion in nominal terms over 99 years
OL,16,Fto secure use of the base.
OL,18,FBut the agreement has faced
OL,19,Fsignificant criticism in both
OL,20,FWestminster and the White House.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
