OL,3,CGovernment denies Chagos Island deal
OL,4,Cis paused after Trump criticism
OL,6,FFalconer told MPs: "There was support
OL,7,Ffrom the US administration for this
OL,8,Ftreaty, which has not changed.
OL,10,F"There clearly has been a statement
OL,11,Ffrom the president of the United
OL,12,FStates more recently, which is very
OL,13,Fsignificant."
OL,15,FHe said the government was "now
OL,16,Fdiscussing those concerns with the
OL,17,FUnited States directly".
OL,19,FMr Falconer told the Commons: "We will
OL,20,Fwe have a process going through
OL,21,FParliament in relation to the treaty.
OL,26,@nD@TOUrD@AOUuD@MO]wD@\OUyD@WO]{D@_OU
