OL,3,CGovernment denies Chagos Island deal
OL,4,Cis paused after Trump criticism
OL,6,F"We will bring that back to Parliament
OL,7,Fat the appropriate time. We are
OL,8,Fpausing for discussions with our
OL,9,FAmerican counterparts."
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FA Foreign, Commonwealth & Development
OL,17,FOffice spokesperson told ITV News:
OL,18,F"There is no pause. We have never set
OL,19,Fa deadline. Timings will be announced
OL,20,Fin the usual way.
