OL,3,CGovernment denies Chagos Island deal
OL,4,Cis paused after Trump criticism
OL,6,F"We are continuing discussions with
OL,7,Fthe US and we have been clear we will
OL,8,Fnot proceed without their support."
OL,10,FDespite the denials, the deal has been
OL,11,Fpaused, the legislation has not been
OL,12,Fdebated in either the Commons or the
OL,13,FLords since January 20, even though it
OL,14,Fis in its final stages.
OL,16,FLast week, Mr Trump described the
OL,17,FChagos Islands deal as "tenuous" and
OL,18,F"no good", just a day after the US
OL,19,Fstate department said it had supported
OL,20,Fthe agreement to hand over the
OL,21,Farchipelago.
